<img width="455" height="526" class="wp-image-1842124" style="width: 600px;" src="https://cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/madam-social.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/madam-social.jpg?width=455&amp;auto_optimize=medium 455w, https://cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/madam-social-260x300.jpg?width=260&amp;auto_optimize=medium 260w" sizes="(max-width: 455px) 100vw, 455px" /> The social media comedienne, Madam Social, is dead. She died on Tuesday, 7th of June, 2022. Her death was announced on her Instagram page. “She can’t be gone! How do I witness that laughter of yours?”, the post read.